tutorial.title: D&D Jakarta: Cara Main D&D Online di Roll20
tutorial.description: Dungeons & Dragons Jakarta! Yuk main online di roll20.net, caranya gampang kok, di video ini saya akan share mengenai hal ini. Join DNDJakarta Discord Server ya di link / discord. Kunjungi website D&D Jakarta di http://www.dndjakarta.com.

tutorial.title: How to Play Dungeons and Dragons | A Quick Beginners Guide
tutorial.description: From creating your character to navigating through epic adventures, this video equips you with the essential knowledge and tips to embark on your own thrilling D&D journey with confidence.

tutorial.title: PANDUAN DND - APA ITU DUNGEON AND DRAGONS ? - EPISODE 1
tutorial.description: Dungeons & Dragons (disingkat D&D atau DnD) adalah sebuah permainan peran (RPG) berjenis fantasy yang diterbitkan oleh Wizards of the Coast. Permainan Dungeons & Dragons pertama, dirancang oleh Gary Gygax dan Dave Arneson, Nah...kalo kalian tertarik mau main, mulai aja dengan tonton video ini.

tutorial.title: HOW TO PLAY DUNGEONS & DRAGONS - A beginners guide to D&D
tutorial.description: Love Critical Role? HighRollers? Rivals of Waterdeep? Always wanted to play D&D but didn't know where to start? This video is a complete introduction to D&D, explaining how the game works, how long it takes, what you need to play as well as dispelling myths about what D&D is and isn't.
